            FUZZ="off"
    VIEW_REPORTS="off"
           SOUND="off"
         ARCHIVE="off"
           SHORT="Updates only Sorcery package management tools v0.1.6"
cat << EOF
Sorcery (v0.1.6)  -  Tools package management by source.

sorcery includes the following files:
  /etc/sorcery/*                    configuration files.
  /usr/doc/sorcery/*                documentation, please read
  /usr/sbin/sorcery                 menu driven interface
  /usr/sbin/leach                   downloads spells' sources (depreciated)
  /usr/sbin/summon		    replacement for leach
  /usr/sbin/cast                    installs  spells
  /usr/sbin/vcast                   installs  spells  verbosely
  /usr/sbin/dispel                  removes   spells
  /usr/sbin/gaze                    provides information about the box
  /var/lib/sorcery/apprentice       spell:/location/binary for launchers
  /var/lib/sorcery/excluded         list of files that are ignored
  /var/lib/sorcery/protected        list of files that will not be deleted
  /var/lib/sorcery/subroutines      common subroutines

  and man pages.

  Updates ONLY the sorcery tools.

EOF
